Susan Damante https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Susan_Damante 0 Susan Damante (born June 17, 1950; formally credited as Susan Damante-Shaw) is an American actress who has starred in various films and television programs. She was first runner-up to Miss California in the Miss America Pageant. She is the mother of Vinessa Shaw and Natalie Shaw (both actresses).
